Package: ShennongData
Type: Package
Title: Lazy R Client for Shennong Data Server
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Songqi", "Duan", , "duan@songqi.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Author: Songqi Duan [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Songqi Duan <duan@songqi.org>
Description: Provides tidyverse-style lazy access to Shennong Data Server
    datasets. Objects returned by sn_load_data() keep only API query state until
    collect(), plotting, or another materializing operation requests data.
